nodes.text: Who's Who in the Outlander Club: It's Ladies' Night

Who's Who in the Outlander Club: It's Ladies' Night was an article appearing in Star Wars: The Official Magazine 54 and Star Wars Insider 75, written by Daniel Wallace with special thanks to Pablo Hidalgo. It provides photos and brief descriptions of over forty patrons of the Outlander Club as seen in Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones.
